title: Fortress
content:
Fortress may also refer to:

  • Black Knights' Fortress, a castle inhabited by black knights entered during Black Knights' Fortress and King's Ransom
    • Black Knights' Fortress, a quest
    • Fortress Guard, the guards around the Black Knights' Fortress
  • Dark Warriors' Fortress, a castle in levels 14, 15 and 16 multi-combat Wilderness north of Falador.
  • Dragonkin fortress, Ungael, an island located in northernmost region of the Lunar Sea, home of Vorkath
  • Zamorak's Fortress, a God chamber in the God Wars Dungeon containing K'ril Tsutsaroth, Balfrug Kreeyath, Tstanon Karlak, and Zakl'n Gritch
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
